'''Jim Shooter''' is a comic book editor and writer. He was Editor-in-Chief of [[Marvel Comics]] from [[1978]] to [[1987]], and was directly involved with many Star Wars comic series, including [[Star Wars (1977)|''Marvel Star Wars'']] and [[Star Wars: Droids (1986)|''Star Wars: Droids'']].

